    KGCMUtil_128
    Utilities for the GF(2^m) field with corresponding extension polynomial: GF (2^128) -> x^128 + x^7 + x^2 + x + 1 The representation is little-endian arrays of 64-bit words
    KGCMUtil_256
    Utilities for the GF(2^m) field with corresponding extension polynomial: GF (2^256) -> x^256 + x^10 + x^5 + x^2 + 1 The representation is little-endian arrays of 64-bit words
    KGCMUtil_512
    Utilities for the GF(2^m) field with corresponding extension polynomial: GF (2^512) -> x^512 + x^8 + x^5 + x^2 + 1 The representation is little-endian arrays of 64-bit words
